txt.en: Defeated many Orc-kind in Eryn Lasgalen.
You have defeated many Orcs in Eryn Lasgalen and have assisted the Elves in their efforts to restore the forest.
'Orcs hide yet in the vales of the Emyn-nu-Fuin. I would ask you to defeat any Orcs that you come across while you are in my domain.'
Orcs can be found scattered throughout Eryn Lasgalen.\n\nKing Thranduil has bade you defeat any Orc-kind you come across.
Orcs hide yet in the vales.
Orcs who escaped the Battle Under the Trees now hide in the vicinity of the Emyn-nu-Fuin.
